DESCRIPTION: Example of how to set up the TamaguiProvider component in a React application, including importing necessary modules and applying a configuration.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tamagui/tamagui/blob/main/code/tamagui.dev/data/docs/intro/installation.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_2

