TITLE: Implementing Root Layout with NextTamaguiProvider
DESCRIPTION: Sets up the root layout component for Next.js app router that includes the NextTamaguiProvider, handling page metadata and the HTML structure.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tamagui/tamagui/blob/main/code/tamagui.dev/data/docs/guides/next-js.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: tsx
