TITLE: SizableText Component Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Details the implementation of SizableText component which provides the foundation for text sizing in Tamagui headings, including font styling variants.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tamagui/tamagui/blob/main/code/tamagui.dev/data/docs/components/headings/1.0.0.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_2

