TITLE: Calculating Spring Animation in TypeScript for Tamagui
DESCRIPTION: This function calculates spring animation parameters based on mass, stiffness, and damping. It returns an object with natural frequency and damping ratio.
SOURCE: https://github.com/tamagui/tamagui/blob/main/code/ui/animate/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: TypeScript
CODE:
```
export function calcSpring(mass = 1, stiffness = 100, damping = 10, velocity = 0) {
  const w0 = Math.sqrt(stiffness / mass)
  const zeta = damping / (2 * Math.sqrt(stiffness * mass))
  return {
    w0,
    zeta,
    wd: w0 * Math.sqrt(1 - zeta ** 2),
    a: 1,
    b: zeta * w0,
  }
}
```

